title: United Kingdom Imports - Tobacco & Manufactured Tobacco Substitutes
description: Imports - Tobacco & Manufactured Tobacco Substitutes in the United Kingdom decreased to 61.40 GBP Million in September from 71.75 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Tobacco & Manufactured Tobacco Substitut in the United Kingdom averaged 40.99 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 189.40 GBP Million in March of 2012 and a record low of 7.07 GBP Million in February of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports Ofbacco & Manufactured Tobacco Substitutes.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
